OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start with
OL,6,Fa touch of frost possible. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells will turn hazy during the day
OL,8,Fas cloud thickens from the west.
OL,9,FFeeling pleasant in any sunshine with
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain pushing in
OL,13,Ffrom the west this evening, mostly
OL,14,Flight and patchy, although the odd
OL,15,Fheavier burst possible overnight.
OL,16,FMilder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
